text: Kanatlarci (, ), according to the 2001 census, is the largest village and second largest settlement in the municipality of Prilep, North Macedonia. It used to be part of the former municipality of Topolčani. ==Demographics== According to the 2002 census, the village had a total of 972 inhabitants.
